        "mean_body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In the supplement industry, 'science-backed' is often a marketing phrase applied to any ingredient that appears in at least one study somewhere. At Bloomli it's a process. Published human data is preferred over animal or in-vitro research. Doses are chosen to match the clinical research — not to look impressive on the label. Every active has a clear role, and we can explain that role in plain language before you buy.</p><p>Hair wellness is gradual by biology — follicles operate on cycles that take months to complete. We don't promise overnight results. What we promise is a formula you can trust, a routine you can maintain, and expectations that are honest from the start.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
